    "This approach encourages users to take necessary precautions in maintaining and using the system correctly.",
    "In the case of highly autonomous AI systems, users may not be expected to monitor them actively.",
    "However, users still have control over the choice to employ AI systems, which justifies assigning them some liability for decisions delegated to AI (Buiten et al., 2023).",
    "Users also benefit from using AI systems.",
    "Allocating costs of harm to the beneficiaries of AI technologies can motivate them to make socially optimal decisions about when and how to use these systems. foot_13"
